name: Falafel Wrap
shortDescription: Crispy falafel balls wrapped in pita bread.
details: Crispy falafel balls made from ground chickpeas and herbs, wrapped in warm pita bread. Served with creamy tahini sauce, fresh lettuce, and tangy pickles for a perfect balance of flavors.

name: Tacos Al Pastor
shortDescription: Spicy pork tacos with pineapple and cilantro.
details: Tender, marinated pork cooked on a vertical spit, served on soft corn tortillas. Topped with sweet pineapple, fresh cilantro, and a squeeze of lime for a burst of flavor.

name: Burger Deluxe
shortDescription: A juicy beef burger with lettuce, tomato, and cheese.
details: Made with 100% organic beef, this burger features a juicy patty, crisp lettuce, ripe tomatoes, and melted cheese, all served on a freshly baked bun. Perfectly paired with golden fries.

name: Pasta Alfredo
shortDescription: Creamy Alfredo sauce with fettuccine pasta.
details: Silky smooth Alfredo sauce made with Parmesan cheese, butter, and cream, tossed with perfectly cooked fettuccine pasta. Garnished with a sprinkle of parsley for a touch of freshness.

name: Churros with Chocolate
shortDescription: Sweet fried dough with cinnamon sugar and chocolate dip.
details: Freshly fried churros, crispy on the outside and soft on the inside, dusted with cinnamon sugar. Served with a rich, velvety chocolate dipping sauce for the ultimate treat.

name: Sushi Platter
shortDescription: A variety of fresh sushi rolls with soy sauce and wasabi.
details: A beautifully arranged platter of sushi rolls, featuring fresh fish, avocado, and cucumber, wrapped in vinegared rice and nori. Served with soy sauce, wasabi, and pickled ginger.

name: Pad Thai
shortDescription: Stir-fried rice noodles with shrimp and tofu.
details: Authentic Pad Thai made with stir-fried rice noodles, succulent shrimp, and crispy tofu. Tossed in a tangy tamarind sauce and garnished with crushed peanuts, fresh lime, and bean sprouts.

name: Chicken Biryani
shortDescription: Spicy chicken biryani with basmati rice.
details: Fragrant basmati rice layered with tender, spiced chicken, caramelized onions, and aromatic spices. Slow-cooked to perfection for a rich and flavorful experience.
